{"tid":2323193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳雲：星期日講道。","createTime":"2020-12-13T03:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T05:58:48.000Z","uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99bfc7c8ff4dc54485c893aef1b17813f9ff35c8","tid":2323193,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"陳雲：星期日講道。朋友在大陸。發現生活如常，好多細路、青年在街場打籃球。<br />\n<br />\n街上冇人戴口罩。只有部分場所如超市貼告示強制要戴，但無人監管，路人也毫不在乎，冇用過健康碼。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，自己玩自己，自己人折磨自己人。點解香港人會喜歡自我虐待？<br />\n<br />\n因為最衰都係陳雲，一早篤爆咗新冠病毒是弱流感，仲講埋答案是要全民檢測和接種致病疫苗，香港人柒咗之後，唯有戴口罩戴到落棺材！<br />\n<br />\n香港人與陳雲鬥氣，而陳雲是佛祖弟子，一直在香港布施慈悲和無畏。<br />\n請問：有什麼人是會與佛祖弟子鬥氣的呢？<br />\n答案：魔。香港人很多是波旬、撒旦的追隨者。<br />\n好多香港人是波旬、撒旦的信徒。認了吧。不認，沒法得到拯救的。<br />\n<br />\n笑拿死 雖然錯唔晒"},{"pid":"901a259b19b10ab16b1ae56ff645886bc5b9689c","tid":2323193,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">扮燒山fans嘅雲糞<br />\n每日開幾個post帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0vOfJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0vOfJ0.jpg&h=d9a57d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGVnkaG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGVnkaG.jpg&h=22e80bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8K3j6QH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8K3j6QH.jpg&h=bc059408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bsF24Co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbsF24Co.jpg&h=1fa7a04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bumBxw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbumBxw9.png&h=314cd63b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gbfbmqv.png\" data-thumbna